This can be electronically
assigned by the administrator of

00:17:15.490 --> 00:17:18.160
your iTunes Connect organization.

00:17:18.870 --> 00:17:22.710
Once we have that signed contract,
we need you to provide three

00:17:22.710 --> 00:17:24.850
additional pieces of information.

00:17:25.020 --> 00:17:28.500
The first are your finance
and legal contacts.

00:17:28.540 --> 00:17:31.640
The second is a bank
account to receive payments.

00:17:31.700 --> 00:17:35.310
Note that even if you plan to
distribute commercially in 62 countries,

00:17:35.320 --> 00:17:37.620
we only need a single
bank account from you.

00:17:37.620 --> 00:17:41.580
Your bank will automatically handle
the currency conversion for you.

00:17:41.730 --> 00:17:44.760
and the last thing we need from
you is your tax information.

00:17:44.820 --> 00:17:48.840
For developers within the United States,
you can electronically submit your

00:17:48.840 --> 00:17:51.820
W-9 form within iTunes Connect.

00:17:51.860 --> 00:17:55.910
And for developers outside the US,
you can download your W-8 bin form from

00:17:55.970 --> 00:18:00.640
iTunes Connect that you'll then need to
fill out and put back in the mail to us.

00:18:02.690 --> 00:18:05.600
To get to your contracts,
log into iTunes Connect,

00:18:05.680 --> 00:18:09.310
click on the upper left
module called Contracts.

